components.templateData:
<a
  appText
  variant="paragraph"
  [routerLink]="'translations'"
  routerLinkActive="active"
  ariaCurrentWhenActive="page"
>
  Keys and Values</a
>

components.name: LanguagePickerComponent
components.templateData:
<select (change)="changeLanguage($event)">
  @for (language of languages(); track $index) {
  <option
    [selected]="languageService.currentLanguage() === language.value"
    [value]="language.value"
  >
    {{ language.key | translate }}
  </option>
  }
</select>

components.name: LoadingCircleComponent
LoadingScreenComponent
NavComponent
ToastComponent
components.templateData:
@if(toastService.isOpen()){ @if(toasts().length > 0) { } } @else { }
@if(toastService.isOpen()) { @for (toast of toasts(); track $index; let idx = $index) {
{{ toast.dateTime | date : "shortTime" }}
@if (toast.correlation_id) { {{ toast.correlation_id }} }

{{ toast.type | uppercase }}

{{ toast.message }}

} }
